name: WAITING
description:
She would come for me but she never did when I asked her to, I begged her to come but I never got an answer, now I'm tired, I can't move, i cant scream, and my legs don't have the same strength as a few years ago. I should have gone to look for her when I longed for our meeting,  but I was afraid and I was not able to do it or to leave my family. The suffering, the sadness that for so many years I had inside me will now end, and death will finally come to look for me

Mp4 1536x2304
